Walton Street Capital, L.L.C. Key Developments

RXR Realty And Walton Street Capital Seeks Minority Stake Sale Of Park Avenue Atrium
Mar 15 17
RXR Realty LLC and Walton Street Capital, L.L.C. are seeking a new equity partner and a recapitalization of office tower known as Park Avenue Atrium, according to the New York Post.


Blackstone Group Seeks to sell The Westin Harbour Island
Jul 29 16
The Blackstone Group L.P. (NYSE:BX) is seeking to sell The Westin Tampa Harbour Island. The hotel was on sale in 2015 but deal never came to fruition. The Westin Harbour Island, which has 299 rooms and 18,000 square feet of meeting space, is said to be under contract to Walton Street Capital, L.L.C. according to the source familiar with the matter and is going to be sold in the later months of 2016.


Walton St. Capital Mexico Presents at HSBC Latin American Investment Summit 2016, Apr-12-2016
Mar 17 16
Walton St. Capital Mexico Presents at HSBC Latin American Investment Summit 2016, Apr-12-2016 . Venue: Ocean Reef Club, 35 Ocean Reef Drive, Key Largo, FL 33037, United States. Speakers: Diego Gutiérrez, Principal & Head of Financing, Federico Martín del Campo, CEO.


